    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/77">Henricus</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Si ecclesiis dei thesaurizare studuerimus,
                        in futuro meritum recipere satis credimus. Quapropter sancte dei ecclesie
                        fidelibus nostrisque omnibus pateat nunc et in posterum, nos pro nostre
                        anime futura recompensatione et ob interventum dilectissime genitricis
                        nostre <persName key="#Queen" ref="#people/365">Agnetis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">imperatricis</rs> auguste iuxta nostre concessionis
                        auctoritatem <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/406"
                            >sancte <placeName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#places/245"
                                >Nouariensi</placeName> ecclesie</orgName>, ubi sanctum Gaudentii
                        corpus requiescit, <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/411"
                            >sancti Felicis</orgName> videlicet que vulgo dicitur Regine <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">abatiam</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/65">Papie</placeName> sitam cum
                        cella Curte veteri nominata cunctisque aliis pertinentiis suis concessisse,
                        ea scilicet ratione ut predicte ecclesie <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>
                        liberam dehinc potestatem habeant inibi abatissam ordinandi, presentis <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">paginae</rs> nostre iussionis literis
                        annotate testimonio. Concedimus itaque <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatum</rs>
                        de <geogName
                            key="#Shores #Mansi #Slave_labour #Castle #Ports #Comitatus #Public_exactions #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/327"><placeName
                                key="#Shores #Mansi #Slave_labour #Castle #Ports #Comitatus #Public_exactions #Teloneum"
                                ref="#places/733">Plumbia</placeName></geogName> cum <rs
                            key="#Shores">ripa</rs> Ticini a loco qui dicitur
                            <placeName>Camaracam</placeName> usque ad <placeName>Petram Mauram
                        </placeName>et alium comitatum de <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Slave_labour #Castle #Ports #Comitatus #Public_exactions #Teloneum"
                            ref="#places/54"><geogName
                                key="#Mansi #Slave_labour #Castle #Ports #Comitatus #Public_exactions #Teloneum"
                                ref="#estates/92">Osola</geogName></placeName> cum sua integritate
                        iuxta auctoritatem nostrorum antecessorum imperatorum, patris scilicet
                        nostri felicis memorie <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/237"
                            >Henrici</persName> imperatoris augusti avique nostri <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/261">Conradi</persName> imperatoris et
                        iterum Henrici imperatoris et <rs key="#Curtes">curtim</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/402"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/835">Grauadona</placeName></geogName> cum curte de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/403"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/838">Vespolate</placeName></geogName> cum utriusque
                        portionibus Vberti atque Vgonis et <rs key="#Castle">castrum</rs> de
                            <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle"
                            ref="#places/839">Vuilingo</placeName> et de <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle"
                            ref="#places/840">Curegio</placeName> cum pertinentiis eorum et duos <rs
                            key="#Mansi">mansos</rs> in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/842"
                            >Garbania</placeName> et quicquid Vbertus Nouariae habet intus et foris
                        et curticellam, que constat in Mathiero, et quicquid tenet in Alizate et in
                            <placeName ref="#places/841"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >Crescia</placeName> et in <placeName ref="#places/843"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >Xuno</placeName>, et quicquid habet Ribaldus in eodem loco et in
                        Belingo et quicquid habet Vgo filius condam Vualonis in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/736">Pernate</placeName> et in
                            <placeName>Terdobiate</placeName> cum suis adiacentiis et
                            <rs>corticellam</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/521"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                                ref="#estates/275">Cauali</geogName></placeName> regis, quam tenet
                        Richardus, cum <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/844">alpe de Otro</placeName>, simul etiam cum <rs
                            key="#Ports">ponte</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Ports #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/846">Varade</placeName> et rocham Vberti de valle Sesedana
                        et omnia predia, que ipse retinet in predicta valle et in <placeName
                            ref="#places/847"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >Seticiano</placeName>, et quartam portionem de curte <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#estates/404"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                                ref="#places/845">Cerro</placeName></geogName> et quicquid Richardus
                        et Vbertus retinent in valle Oxula et circa <rs key="#Lakes">lacum</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            ref="#places/836">sancti Iulii</placeName> in circuitu, preterea
                        quicquid nefandissimi interfectores advocati, Vgo scilicet et Bruno filii
                        condam Bonihominis et Richardus filius item Richardi et Albertus et
                        Rustichellus mobile seu immobile proprium habuerunt, iuxta bannum carissimi
                        genitoris nostri imperatoris Henrici et iuxta nostrum quoque bannum legali
                        sanctione nostraque regia auctoritate publicamus et publicata sancte
                        Nouariensi ecclesie perpetuo iure concedimus et confirmamus, eo videlicet
                        ordine ut omnes prenominate ecclesie pontifices predictam sancti Felicis
                        abatiam que vulgo Regine dicitur et duos predictos comitatus cum <rs
                            key="#Teloneum">teloneis</rs> et <rs key="#Districtio">publicis omnibus
                            functionibus r</rs>egie potestatis et prescriptas curtes cum castris
                        earum et simul cum vallibus et ponte ac alpe et mansos superius relatos cum
                            <rs key="#Slave">servis</rs> et utriusque sexus familiis et omnem
                        possessionem Vberti et Ricardi circa lacum sancti Iulii habentium earumque
                        pertinentiis et adiacentiis habeant teneant firmiterque possideant;
                        habeantque licentiam legali sive duellali diffinitione emersuras
                        contentiones dirimere, nostra nostrorumque successorum et totius dignitatis
                        seu officii hominum contradictione remota. Si quis igitur huius nostre
                        corroborationis statuto contrahire temptaverit, C talentorum auri reus
                        existat, medietatem nobis et medietatem eidem ecclesie persolvenda. Et ut
                        verius credatur, nostro sigillo iussimus insigniri. Signum domni Henrici
                        quarti regis. <persName><name>Uoicberdus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> vice <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Archbishops" ref="#people/1306">Annonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicancellarii</rs> recognovit. Data est idibus
                        aprilis anno incarnacionis dominice millesimo sexagesimo, indicione decima,
                        anno autem ordinacionis domni Henrici quarti regis sexto, regni vero quarto;
                        actum <placeName>Gozlarie</placeName>; in dei nomine feliciter amen. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
